productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Zoa has one of these. She works as a scribe and she says it looks wide.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 kilogram!!!
heard about this on melodic death metal radio, decided to give it a try.
It only works when I'm New Caledonia.
i use it from now on when i'm in my safehouse.
